{
  "name": "Breath of Thunder Kami",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to collect and manifest lightning release chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The lightning release chakra begins to collect and spark off of your weapon and body with violent jolts. You prepare for a powerful singular forward slash as your lightning follows behind you in the image of a beast of your description.</p><p>Select one creature you can see within range. Move yourself into a space adjacent to the chosen creature that can hold you. Make one melee Taijutsu attacks using your weapon, dealing your [weapons damage] + 6d12 lightning damage. If the target has any ranks of the Shocked condition, you make your attacks at advantage. If your beats the creatures AC by 10 or more, the creature cannot take a reaction until the end of the current turn, and you ignore any Damage Reduction they are benefiting from.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d12</p>",
